item.title: CVE-2023-3813|2023-07-21T02:04:26.822Z -- artbees%2F -- jupiter%20x%20core
item.description: The Jupiter X Core plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to arbitrary file downloads in versions up to, and including, 2.5.0. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attackers to download the contents of arbitrary files on the server, which can contain sensitive information. The requires the premium version of the plugin to be activated.
